HTML/Webstes, Years of Experience: 2 Capable of Doing: Anything Good With Forums: Yes (VERY) When Available?: Pretty Much all the time, I have school but im on the computer most of my nights. But i can Do RSPS :)
Server Coding, Year of Experience: 3 Capable of Doing: Most things, can fix most glitches, Create shops, Npcs, Training Zones, commands, Donator only items, buy X, etc. When available: Pretty Much all the time, I have school but im on the computer most of my nights. More information about myself: Well, I do football on a team, and im one of the best running back's on my team. I do boxing with people who are 2 years older then me. And i also Do Bmx Biking.
